  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Outsource Manager",
  "description": "<p>- Lead team of Outsource Assistants and Seniors</p>\n<p>- Provide guidance to team members</p>\n<p>- Book-keeping and preparation of management accounts</p>\n<p>- Preparation of Statutory report (Financial Statements and Notes to the accounts)</p>\n<p>- Preparation of custom reporting packages based on client requirements</p>\n<p>- Where clients are audited, provide support with respect to services provided to the client</p>\n<p>- Cash management and payment processing</p>\n<p>- GST preparation and filing</p>\n<p>- Payroll processing</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preparation of payroll details (including calculation of OT, allowances etc.)</li>\n  <li>Payroll disbursement</li>\n  <li>Leave management</li>\n  <li>Preparation of IR8A and IR21</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Handle portfolio of clients, including assignment of jobs to team members</p>\n<p>- Responsible for billings and debtor management for portfolio</p>\n<p>- Review work by Assistants and Seniors</p>\n<p>- Managing team workload to meet client deadlines</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Where possible or required, this would include negotiation with the client on deadlines and corresponding fee adjustments</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Propose resolution steps for issues that may arise with clients</p>\n<p>- Report to director on the following</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Issues that arise with clients</li>\n  <li>Anticipated issues that may arise (eg Deadline not able to be met)</li>\n  <li>Time spent by team on jobs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>- A degree in accountancy and/or equivalent professional qualification</p>\n<p>- At least 5 years of relevant experience from a professional services firm in a Business Process Outsourcing (Client Accounting) environment</p>\n<p>- Proficient with accounting software</p>\n<p>- Meticulous with good accuracy and attention to detail</p>\n<p>- Good communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>- Good knowledge and understanding of Singapore requirements on accounting, GST and payroll</p>",
